{"tid":498027,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[單車] 4屆環法總冠軍Chris Froome藥檢未過 恐遭禁賽","createTime":"2017-12-13T11:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T11:24:37.000Z","uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"071db312d8b35133f247a6b1688bb0492fa10490","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/12c3ce556cf8e7a7c150d7d149118241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F12c3ce556cf8e7a7c150d7d149118241.jpg&h=b4a728a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年對於Chris Froome來說，是一個豐收的賽季，連續獲得環法（Tour de France）和環西的總冠軍榮譽，使他成為繼1978年之後，第一位在一年內同時贏得環法和環西的車手。<br />\n<br />\n國際單車總會（UCI）今天表示，Chris Froome在9月舉行的環西班牙單車賽（Vuelta e Espana）期間，沒有通過藥物檢驗。<br />\n<br />\nChris Froome曾經贏得2013、2015、2016以及2017年的環法冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n隸屬英國天空車隊（Team Sky）的Chris Froome，體內被驗出超過世界反興奮劑機構（WADA）准許份量1倍的治療哮喘的藥物沙丁胺醇（Salbutamol）。<br />\n<br />\n國際單車總會已經要求Chris Froome提供更多訊息，但並沒有將他禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n這份9月的尿樣檢測結果為什麼直至現在才公佈，相信天空車隊希望找到合理解釋，但是一旦失敗，Chris Froome或將失去環西總冠軍的榮譽，同時也有被禁賽的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n早在2007年，就曾有意大利車手（Alessandro Petacchi）因為沙丁胺醇過量被禁賽12個月，並被除去其在同年環意5個賽段冠軍的榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n天空車隊表示，Chris Froome從小就飽受哮喘之苦，也曾宣布他在接受治療。車隊指出，這份藥檢通知並不意味著他已經違反任何規定。"},{"pid":"430bef05514f1b48534bac5920e254f8c3a46196","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce3ca530a1103822f974e1ea84ecc1b9b9c7ea8","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b167aef03a423eed744e78c3cab27805fe0d6b","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66c127a8a83e58a5ba8e1c664164cdb46271595","tid":498027,"uid":126502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"佢今年係屈機到無對手"},{"pid":"9c4eb7918b924f4fcee28ec62c52d08ad5473db1","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e123cc70f5c5d84ef61d922d1c896706f7d0d67c","tid":498027,"uid":154174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢今年係屈機到無對手</blockquote><br />\n環法都無咁屈啦喎，一個分站都無"},{"pid":"6ea5bfe35214f657c9043c2eea035c54d6397f5e","tid":498027,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"有哮喘都咁撚勁呀"},{"pid":"84afd623a4ef75e58303c5821a971cd15a71164e","tid":498027,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"其實係咪個個呢啲爬山單車手都有食藥"},{"pid":"7c62f237071119a79409ef5a07739896f00ecf17","tid":498027,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"單車唔係個個都食藥架咩"},{"pid":"a0f424a839504d485d285e7211cc0e8afbf1268b","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bbbc78174b67e37cc7961e296141758979beb7","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>【藥檢超標】Chris Froome 單車生涯「一子錯，滿盤皆落索」？</strong><br />\n<br />\n最近 UCI 提出了「不利的分析結果」（Adverse Analytical Finding），指 Chris Froome 於今年 9 月份環西班牙第 18 站賽事後的尿液樣本含超標的沙丁胺醇（Salbutamol）， 2,000ng/ml是限制含量的一倍。<br />\n<br />\n而在UCI的醫療使用豁免（Theraputic Use Exemption）規定裡頭，如果24小時內，沙丁胺醇最大的吸入量不超過1600ng/ml，或是12小時內不超過800ng/ml，那麼是可以不需要事先申請。<br />\n<br />\n他跟Sky車隊並未依規定事先申請，於是成了這次禁藥疑雲爆發的主因。<br />\n<br />\n而被爆出超標的環西第十八站，剛好就是Froome與當時主要競爭對手Vincenzo Nibali大幅拉開秒差的一站，更是讓整起事件充滿揣測。<br />\n<br />\n事情會由 Legal Anti-Doping Services及另一全獨立的委員會決定會不會展開聆訊，真的走到這一步的話，Froome的環西冠軍隨時化為煙。<br />\n<br />\nFroome與Sky車隊能做的，不外乎是準備足夠的資料，來說明沙丁胺醇用量完全合乎規定，而檢驗超標的原因是因為複雜的生理與藥物問題，而影響了沙丁胺醇的代謝。<br />\n<br />\n或者是接受藥物代謝動力學（Pharmacokinetics）的測試，來證實Froome服用沙丁胺醇的劑量與之後代謝殘餘量的相對關係，因為有不少測試結果顯示，即便受試者使用了最低劑量的藥劑，但仍有可能會被驗出超標的結果。"},{"pid":"1a696140252cae08a811b1e99012941f398325b4","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0778458b31963a9fa22bc1584936fa194810ae4","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef97e1ac0d22d25a54b694f2d96766186bd42170","tid":498027,"uid":144844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"我最期待...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從有左sky/froome, 環法已經變到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好懷念schleck大戰contador<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b744bfd223031bd48e1644fa2d0a56c435bf32","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2dcdc0363b7c998da871ce6648375f5c2fda94","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7e42af3556841b9ab93d11fe46278985a5cc3e","tid":498027,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"話無都唔信 走岩士唐舊路"},{"pid":"389d59699927ba8aa3df650803375501554a701c","tid":498027,"uid":28170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩買左佢地個team sky車架，係咪要賤賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f159fb46224e96e68883e4e1153242f94401ef98","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ec1f611d7bbd95292162d1046c824cd02f4653","tid":498027,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"佢仍然決定今年出戰環意同環法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33534721c7f07f5ace5dd980220604281f0035a2","tid":498027,"uid":30464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66c127a8a83e58a5ba8e1c664164cdb46271595","tid":498027,"uid":126502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"佢今年係屈機到無對手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"環西後段都踩得無咁輕鬆喇<br />\n世錦賽都開始出現疲態<br />\n<br />\n不過支持天空隊星散"},{"pid":"55a329eed53beb532b6135a270d06feb7475d57f","tid":498027,"uid":1386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d209a845f24bebbcc2eba2ee3a2722245aec67d3","tid":498027,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"幾年前60分鐘時事雜誌講<br />\n天空車隊好似成隊都用改裝電動單車"}]}